step 1 - run instance and install docker 
Step 2 -  run three images a - docker run -d -p 80:80 --name mynginx nginx 
                           b - docker run hello-world
                           c - docker run centos 
step 3 - lifecycle 
a - docker top (conatiner id)
b - docker stats (container id )
c - docker pause (container id)
d - docker unpause 
i - docker start 
e - docker rm -f 
f - docker kill (conatiner id )
